HEADWORD: Quadricornous
<hw>Quad`ri*cor"nous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Quadri-</ets> + L. <ets>cornu</ets> horn: cf. F.
<ets>quadricorne</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Having four
horns, or hornlike organs; <as>as, a <ex>quadricornous</ex>
beetle</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
